# Git Commit Messages

- Always start the subject line with a relevant [gitmoji](https://gitmoji.dev/)
- Follow the **50/72 rule**:
  - Subject line: max 50 characters (including the emoji)
  - Body lines: wrap at 72 characters
- Separate subject from body with a blank line

## Examples

```
✨ Add Mixpanel analytics integration

Set up SDK init, user identification on auth
state changes, and event tracking for sign-in,
errors, purchases, and conversions.
```

```
🐛 Fix auth redirect loop on login
```
